","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"sup","offset":77,"length":2}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3eb32","text":"\nApproximately 10mg tissue was minced with sterilized scissors on ice.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a2mo5","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"1jmde","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"0D897860A1E111EDB19F5DA2FCB8E473","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":165}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"a7njs","text":"Add 350 µl Buffer PBS and 15 µl SDS Lysis Buffer and shake for 30s.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a1fi7","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"24f9e","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":30,"guid":"72643730A1E011EDB19F5DA2FCB8E473","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}}}}

After brief centrifugation, incubate at 56°C for 10 min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"66c2e","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"74n0a","text":"    ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":1,"offset":0,"length":1},{"key":2,"offset":2,"length":1}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":60,"guid":"D61D63F0A1E011EDB19F5DA2FCB8E473","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}},"1":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"0618DE40A1E111EDB19F5DA2FCB8E473","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"56","unit":10}},"2":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":600,"guid":"D85C5770A1E011EDB19F5DA2FCB8E473","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"dunka","text":"Add 350 µl Buffer P-D, vortex for 30s to mix well, and centrifuge at 12,000×g for 10 min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"tl9p","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"4n17i","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":1,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"1pv2v","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":30,"guid":"1BEF8930A1E111EDB19F5DA2FCB8E473","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}},"1":{"type":"shaker","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":600,"error_shaker":false,"error_temperature":false,"guid":"A16D94D0A29A11ED883459AA6C170B9B","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"scientificNotation":{"shaker":false,"temperature":false},"shaker":"12000","start":null,"temperature":"","temperatureUnit":10,"unit":33}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"77msc","text":"Discard the filtrate, put the preparation tube back into the original 2 ml centrifuge tube, add 500µl Buffer W1, and centrifuge at 12,000×g for 1 min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"72ldq","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"6idla","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"shaker","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":60,"error_shaker":false,"error_temperature":false,"guid":"C2D4C260A29A11ED883459AA6C170B9B","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"scientificNotation":{"shaker":false,"temperature":false},"shaker":"12000","start":null,"temperature":"","temperatureUnit":10,"unit":33}}}}
